    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a limited-slip M-differential. The chassis dynamics are preserved with recent subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings, ensuring peak torsional rigidity. Mechanical maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive VANOS service and recent valve clearance adjustment. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the car remains a mechanically robust specimen of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era. It sits on staggered Style 67 wheels wrapped in high-performance rubber, ready for the apex.",
